WEBVTT

00:00.926 --> 00:02.616
<i>Previously on Damages...</i>

00:02.727 --> 00:04.590
<i>I saw your
client on Charlie Rose.</i>

00:04.653 --> 00:06.183
<i>His English is better
than his French.</i>

00:06.317 --> 00:09.544
<i>Mr. Coupet, did you personally
oversee the development of</i>

00:09.615 --> 00:11.561
<i>a vaccine called Tranzec?</i>

00:11.660 --> 00:14.574
<i>We conduct clinical
trials for every drug we develop.</i>

00:14.656 --> 00:18.266
<i>Did you ever have occasion
to hear the term, "adverse event"?</i>

00:18.350 --> 00:21.803
<i>A wrongful death suit was filed against
you and High Star in federal court.</i>

00:21.893 --> 00:23.712
<i>The plaintiff's attorney
is Ellen Parsons.</i>

00:23.810 --> 00:26.816
<i>The brief lists a single
witness, Christopher Sanchez.</i>

00:26.883 --> 00:28.618
<i>Mr. Sanchez
came forward as a witness.</i>

00:28.687 --> 00:31.304
<i>He claimed that High Star was
involved in illegal activity</i>

00:31.364 --> 00:33.142
<i>that led to the
deaths of three men.</i>

00:33.233 --> 00:35.027
<i>I never liked
that last mission.</i>

00:35.097 --> 00:38.447
<i>Lawsuit's been filed.
The company cannot have you talking.</i>

00:38.540 --> 00:40.344
<i>Mr. Sanchez, in
previous conversations, do you</i>

00:40.428 --> 00:43.916
<i>recall stating that you were
involved in an illegal operation?</i>

00:44.004 --> 00:45.534
<i>I don't ever
recall saying that.</i>

00:46.019 --> 00:47.895
<i>What are you doing?
I told them what you wanted!</i>

00:49.982 --> 00:51.154
<i>They got him to lie.</i>

00:51.227 --> 00:53.549
<i>I think they were going
after somebody over there.</i>

